description:
** New listing! See this house! **
** Available for leases starting December 1. **
** Don't miss this RENOVATED classic 2-story Philly row house in a great Pennsport location; it's around the corner from Herman's and Pennsport Beer Boutique! *
328 Earp Street
Pennsport / South Philly / Queen Village Adj / Italian Market Adj
Available: from 12/1/22
Monthly Rent: $1695
Lease: 1 year original term, then month-to-month w/Winter Term
Property features:
- Recent front exterior rehab including painting, house number, door hardware, etc;
- Modern "Euro" Kitchen with white cabinets & stainless/glass cabinet doors, black countertop & glass mini-subway tile backsplash;
APPLIANCES -- refrigerator, gas stove, dishwasher, microwave oven (range hood), washing machine, dryer;
- Refinished ORIGINAL HARDWOOD FLOOR on the first floor;
- SOLID TIGERWOOD HARDWOOD FLOORING on the second floor!
- BATHROOM includes new tub, vanity, medicine cabinet, Italian tile floor;
- Fantastic WALK-OUT DECK off the 2nd flr Rear Bedroom;
- Super large brick-paved outdoor patio;
- Exterior front gate provides direct access to the back patio without going through the house;
- AND MORE!
Location, location, location...
You're in the center of the best of PENNSPORT.
HERMAN'S COFFEE is around the corner. PENNSPORT BEER BOUTIQUE a few steps further. CAFFE VALENTINO delivers Italian fine dining. Prefer fried chicken and homemade donuts? The original FEDERAL DONUTS is in the neighborhood. Check out GOOEY LOOIE'S for monster hoagies. Don't miss the Vietnamese, Chinese, Korean & Mexican restaurants, supermarkets & stores up and down Washington Avenue, Front Street to Broad Street. Target Superstore, Snyder & Front Sts + Ikea & Lowe's! Walk to the historic ITALIAN MARKET & PAT'S & GENO'S CHEESESTEAKS. Also walk to South Street's shopping & restaurants. Pennsport is the home to Philadelphia's Mummers; "2" Street, just 2 blocks east, hosts street parties throughout the year.
Having a cat at the house is OK; pet addendum, deposit, and $10 monthly fee.
** To schedule a showing, please email from this listing or text or call  show contact info
. **
